FUNCTION() - DERP OS man page

Name -------------------
FUNCTION() - <BRIEF DESCRIPTION OF THE FUNCTION

Synopsis ---------------

#include "gl.h"

void draw_line( Uint32 x, Uint32 y, Uint32 x2, Uint32 y2, pixel p );

Description ------------

The draw_line function draws a horizontal or verticle line from ( x, y ) to ( x2, y2 )
with the color of the pixel(p).

Return Value -----------

No return value, side effects are a line in the screen buffer.

Errors -----------------

I beleive that this function is from a very old version and may no longer work.
